Section 1: "WHY IT MATTERS" (Top Row, 3 Horizontal Cards)
- "Single Responsibility" with a target icon, "Typed Contracts" with a shield icon, "Atlas Composes" with a bot icon

Section 2: "THE COST" (Middle Row, Side-by-Side Comparison)
- Left Box (Red Theme): "ANTI-PATTERN — God Action Does Everything". Shows a red status pill "DANGER — ANTI-PATTERN".
- Right Box (Green Theme): "BEST PRACTICE — Single-Purpose Typed Action". Shows a green status pill "SUCCESS — BEST PRACTICE".

